    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are a font of energy that offers respite from injuries. You have a pool of healing energy represented by a number of d6s equal to half your druid level (rounded down).</p>\n<p>As a bonus action, you can choose one creature you can see within 120 feet of you and spend any number of those dice. Roll the spent dice and add them together. The target regains a number of hit points equal to the total. The target also gains 1 temporary hit point per die spent.</p>\n<p>You regain all expended dice when you finish a long rest.</p>",
